      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The engine runs smoothly with no unusual noises, and the transmission shifts reliably through all gears. While the exterior and interior show some minor signs of normal wear, such as light surface scratches and slight upholstery aging, the car is mechanically sound and ready for regular use. It offers a comfortable ride and serves as a dependable option for anyone seeking a quality pre-owned vehicle.",
